Title: My Minimal Monorepo Setup with ZX
Description: fastify-vite is a Fastify plugin, perhaps slowly evolving into a mini framework, that enables client application SSR for Fastify using a variety of client frameworks like Vue and React. At its core, fastify-vite is a simple Fastify route handler factory that will generate a renderer based on the configured Vite build. It has some additional utilities, like project blueprints for the renderer you're using, but in essence all it does is register Vite-flavored Fastify route handlers for you, both in development mode (enabling hot reload) and for production.
